title: Rand Paul sees dismal third quarter fundraising numbers
text: GOP presidential candidate Rand Paul -- once seen as a potential top tier candidate for his party's nomination -- raised just $2.5 million last fundraising quarter, according to a campaign filing released Thursday by Federal Election Commission.
